divs: sighting detailsi was letting my dog out and it was kinda bright out because the moon was really bright and it was not really cloudy at the time. i first noticed the object because i heard an owl and i looked to the tree then i noticed this odd looking structure in the sky. it was pretty far away but i could see little flashing lights in this odd pattern, and this black\dark blue object was moving north and it seemed to be going rising because the lights got farther and father away. then about a minute after that a group of black military helicopters and this large black plane were flying north following the way the ufo went.
Summary: Large solid ship, alot of flashing lights in pattern. 4-5 black helicopters in sky after it was gone.
